dict.string: Add album or playlist to your Alfred Playlist
Search in your playlists for tracks, artists, and albums
Play the previous track in Spotify

on alfred_script(q)
tell application "Spotify" if sound volume is less than or equal to 0 then set sound volume to 100 else set sound volume to 0 end if end tell
end alfred_script
Set the Spotify Volume to Maximum

on alfred_script(q)
tell application "Spotify" set sound volume to 100 end tell
end alfred_script

on alfred_script(q)
tell application "Spotify" set sound volume to 50 end tell
end alfred_script
Current track will be added to Alfred Playlist or My Music
Add current track to Alfred Playlist or My Music

on alfred_script(q)
tell application "Spotify" if shuffling enabled is true then if shuffling is true then set shuffling to false return "Shuffle is disabled." else set shuffling to true return "Shuffle is enabled." end if else return "Shuffling is not currently enabled." end if end tell
end alfred_script
